{"tid":2318443,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"港島西區一房上車盤海景高層荀盤","createTime":"2020-12-09T10:31:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-09T10:46:56.000Z","uid":6297,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"29d67338a5f6178f2d3fb3fb18c5032328b7d456","tid":2318443,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T10:31:04.000Z","msg":"西營盤薈臻高層D室，實用面積約328方呎，建築面積約494方呎，採一房間隔，望開揚市景及部份海景。單位放盤約5個月，原叫價780萬元，經議價後減價47萬元或約6%，最後以733萬元交吉易手，折合實用面積呎價約22,348元，折合建築面積呎價約14,838元。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，原業主在2012年10月，以約800.5萬元買入上述單位，持貨8年，現沽出轉手帳面虧損約67.5萬元或約8%。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上述為薈臻本月首宗二手成交個案，大廈現時約有11個二手盤源提供，最低入場費由約680萬元起。<br />\n<br />\n12年買都住咗咁耐，又可以避開樓價大起大落，未計俾利息都係用幾十萬，一個字 荀"},{"pid":"fa4047551b9fbff1500a2f400ae0a162a28e9a9e","tid":2318443,"uid":112862,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T10:33:16.000Z","msg":"當交租都有賺啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n買樓根本冇得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9945c7ff0d4472d1346d4be230df3e98d50e3fe","tid":2318443,"uid":235727,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T10:34:06.000Z","msg":"中西區不嬲二手舊樓先會有明顯升幅<br />\n一手賣得太貴"},{"pid":"27873b65bfa67f15f129d5bf658ab4283ecd52d9","tid":2318443,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T10:36:24.000Z","msg":"12年800萬買寶翠園，依家都執唔少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d93c34c1d14e78bdc36472165c27fdfe31152bf","tid":2318443,"uid":235727,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"27873b65bfa67f15f129d5bf658ab4283ecd52d9","tid":2318443,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T10:36:24.000Z","msg":"12年800萬買寶翠園，依家都執唔少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T10:39:25.000Z","msg":"印象中12年寶翠園全部已經過千"},{"pid":"e13aeff7dc045adc97b0ae76ffec1d5954ff733a","tid":2318443,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dis